TODAY JUNE 27, 2018 ABOUT 2.10PM I ORDER A MEDIUM  SOUP  AND THE SOUP GIRL ADDED SHRIMP AND WANTED TO WRITE 2.50 ON THE LID , WHEN I ASKED QUOTE " WHAT ARE YOU DOING ITS 1.50 QUOTE" SHE LOOKED AT THE SERVERS AND THEY LOOKED AT HER AND SAID 2.50 . I WAS SHOCKED AND ASKED THE CASHIER QUOTE"YOU SEE ME HERE EVERYDAY , YOU KNOW THEY ALWAYS CHARGE AN EXTRA $1.50 WHY ARE'NT YOU SAYING ANYTHING , SHE WAS AFRAID AND DID'NT SAY ANYTHING , I LEFT THE SOUP AND GOT A MEDIUM WITHOUT THE SHRIMP . THIS PLACE IS UNPROFESSIONAL TO CHANGE THE PRICE FROM ONE DAY TO ANOTHER . I WILL POST EVERYDAY . TILL SOMEONE RESPONDS BACK , I'M DEFINITEDLY NOT AN IDIOT AND HAVE PROOF ON MY STATEMENT OF THE PRICE OF MEDUIM SOUP AND EXTRA CHARGE OF 1.50  .
